The paper deals with natural language processing and knowledge management, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses a question answering task, which falls under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of derivational resources and morphological analysis suggests a possible connection to the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NE), which often employ similar techniques.
